{"tid":1621483,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"林奠今日推蒙面法係想我地玩First Purge?","createTime":"2019-10-04T13:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T13:50:46.000Z","uid":172102,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"66445124f688a18d48d4fc59e059ce4af93274ed","tid":1621483,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:50:46.000Z","msg":"一過十二點，就唔俾再蒙面，<br />\n即係deadline前可以盡情蒙面，<br />\n仲要激起各區大型嚴重示威，<br />\n平時唔出黎嘅都出哂黎，<br />\n廢鐵已廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有休班狗同黑驚開始真正受難，<br />\n係咪想啟動一次《港定殺戮日》？<br />\n<br />\n林奠呢個英國間諜可謂用心良苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港獨之母啊港獨之母，知唔知first purge 個slogan係「A Nation Reborn 」啊？咁想終蟈 Reborn啊？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3rDmtr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3rDmtr.jpg&h=9ccae120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://blackgirlnerds.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/purge3.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblackgirlnerds.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Fpurge3.jpg&d=HXevA6ue1FLA%2Fu9R3J04Lj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=b0c21bb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://blackgirlnerds.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/purge3.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/digitalspyuk.cdnds.net/18/27/1530787006-the-purge.jpg?resize=480:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fdigitalspyuk.cdnds.net%2F18%2F27%2F1530787006-the-purge.jpg%3Fresize%3D480%3A%2A&h=e3cca983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pixel.nymag.com/imgs/daily/vulture/2018/11/06/06-the-purge.w700.h700.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpixel.nymag.com%2Fimgs%2Fdaily%2Fvulture%2F2018%2F11%2F06%2F06-the-purge.w700.h700.jpg&h=3f50e2ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/s--cvwYS_U4--/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_800/rabkz79phkcwll3qlisw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kinja-img.com%2Fgawker-media%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fs--cvwYS_U4--%2Fc_scale%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_80%2Cw_800%2Frabkz79phkcwll3qlisw.jpg&h=3e9f2868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係The Purge 系列入面，天光Siren響起前，都無人確保到會發生咩事，狗隻記得千祈唔好出街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}